      "message": "Hi Seewai, thanks for the update.\n\nYour PoCs surfaced many points to discuss. Thank you for this work!\n\nIMO, design decision points include:\n\n- Associating vars to context.Context vs. making vars globally accessible without context.Context\n- Scattering registrations to multiple files/packages vs. keeping registrationgs in a single file/package\n- Whether to support typed runtime variables (e.g. int)\n- Whether to support safe access (typo caught in build-time)\n\nI\u0027d like you to discuss these points in your design doc.\n",
